These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  manager, lawyer, entrepreneur
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, skateboard, train
1. the person driving the roller is not to the left of the person driving the train##8
2. the entrepreneur is somewhere to the right of the person driving the train##5
3. the person driving the train is between the lawyer and the entrepreneur##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |     3      |
| Job         | lawyer | manager   | entrepreneur |
| Transport   | skateboard | train | roller        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, milk, sprite
3 different pets are kept: frog, mouse, goldfish
1. the person drinking juice is somewhere between the person drinking sprite and the owner of the frog##7
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
3. the owner of the mouse is not to the right of the person drinking juice##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |     3      |
| Beverage   | sprite | juice   | milk   |
| Pet        | mouse | goldfish | frog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-3::.
There 3 different types of food: spinach, watermelon, peach
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, airplane, ship
1. the person eating spinach is not to the left of the person driving the airplane##8
2. the person eating peach is somewhere between the person eating spinach and the person driving the skateboard##7
3. the person eating peach is not to the left of the person driving the ship##8
4. the person eating peach is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |
| Food        | watermelon | peach | spinach |
| Transport   | skateboard       | ship     | airplane         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  writer, journalist, security-guard
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, superhero, action
1. the security-guard is not to the right of the journalist##8
2. the security-guard is on the right of the writer##1
3. the person watching western movies is somewhere between the person watching superhero movies and the writer##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Job           | writer | security-guard | journalist |
| Movie-Genre   | action  | western | superhero    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, documentary, spy
3 different pets are kept: hamster, frog, ferret
1. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3
3. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
4. the person watching documentary movies is not to the right of the person watching western movies##8
5. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
6. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | spy | western |
| Pet           | frog    | ferret      | hamster  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-6::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, musician, librarian
3 different pets are kept: lizard, frog, rabbit
1. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the architect##5
2. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the right of the architect##5
3. the librarian is not to the right of the owner of the lizard##8
4. the musician is on the left of the architect##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |   2    |       3        |
| Job   | musician | architect | librarian |
| Pet   | rabbit        | frog   | lizard     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-7::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, cola, soy-milk
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, social-worker, scientist
1. the social-worker is between the scientist and the person drinking soy-milk##2
2. the person drinking cola is not to the left of the scientist##8
3. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the left of the scientist##8
4. the scientist is the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | mirinda | cola | soy-milk |
| Job        | scientist      | social-worker    | nurse |

