2. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the right of the person who's sport is parkour##8
3. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
4. the german is not to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |
| Nationality   | thai | polish    | german |
| Sport         | lacrosse  | volleyball | parkour |

