.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-9::.
There 3 different types of food: corn, pepper, avocado
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, family, spy
1. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the person watching spy movies##5
2. the person eating avocado is somewhere to the left of the person eating pepper##5
3. the person watching animation movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching family movies is not to the right of the person eating corn##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |
| Food          | avocado | corn  | pepper |
| Movie-Genre   | animation     | family | spy   |

