.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, milk, cola
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, water-polo, soccer
1. the person drinking cola is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8
3. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##5
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage   | milk | cola        | iced-tea    |
| Sport      | water-polo  | soccer | cricket |

