.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-14::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, fanta, hot-chocolate
The people have 3 different hobbies: sudoku, singing, drawing
1. the person drinking fanta is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person drinking soy-milk##7
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |     3      |
| Beverage   | fanta     | hot-chocolate | soy-milk   |
| Hobby      | drawing | singing | sudoku |

