.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-17::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, gospel, dubstep
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, climbing, soccer
1. the fan of dubstep is not to the right of the person who's sport is climbing##8
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the fan of dubstep is between the fan of gospel and the fan of soul##2
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
5. the fan of gospel is not to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Music-Genre   | soul       | dubstep      | gospel |
| Sport         | golf | climbing | soccer     |

