2. the owner of the turtle is not to the right of the owner of the turtle##8
3. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the person eating pear##5
4. the person eating tomato is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3
5. the person eating pear is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |     2     |     3      |
| Food   | lime | pear | tomato    |
| Pet    | turtle   | pony      | rat |

