.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-19::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, martial-arts, scientific
There are 3 different nationalities: american, russian, indian
1. the person watching scientific movies is in the middle##1
2. the indian is the person watching scientific movies##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the person watching romance movies and the person watching martial-arts movies##7
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is not to the left of the american##8
5. the american is not to the left of the person watching scientific movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | romance   | scientific    | martial-arts  |
| Nationality   | russian | indian | american |

