.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, fishing, writing
There are 3 different nationalities: thai, pakistani, dutch
1. the pakistani is somewhere between the dutch and the person who's hobby is writing##7
2. the thai is not to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##8
3. the thai is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |      3      |
| Hobby         | puzzles | fishing | writing |
| Nationality   | dutch  | pakistani    | thai    |

 